casebody.data:
Wanda TAYLOR, Plaintiff-Appellant, v. Chris DeMARCO, Jeff Watson, Defendants-Appellees. No. 09-14835

Non-Argument Calendar.

United States Court of Appeals, Eleventh Circuit. April 19, 2010. Ralph Goldberg, Decatur, GA, for Plaintiff-Appellant. Eddie Snelling, Jr., Attorney General’s Office, Atlanta, GA, for Defendants-Appel-lees. Before BARKETT, WILSON and FAY, Circuit Judges. PER CURIAM:

Having reviewed the record and the briefs of the parties, we find no reversible error in the district court’s order granting *965summary judgment in favor of Chris De-Marco and Jeff Watson.

AFFIRMED.
